import React from "react"; import "./AnalysisDisplay.css"; // Ensure you have this CSS file for styling const AnalysisDisplay = ({ totalROI = 0, numberOfTrades = 0, sharpeRatio = 0, netPL = 0, cashBalance = 0, winningTrades = 0, losingTrades = 0, winRate = 0, averageWin = 0, averageLoss = 0, riskRewardRatio = 0, maximumDrawdown = 0, }) => { return (

Total ROI

{totalROI.toFixed(2)}%

Number of Trades

{numberOfTrades}

Sharpe Ratio

{sharpeRatio.toFixed(2)}

Net P/L

${netPL.toFixed(2)}

Cash Balance

${cashBalance.toFixed(2)}

Winning Trades

{winningTrades}

Losing Trades

{losingTrades}

Win Rate

{winRate.toFixed(2)}%

Average Win

${averageWin.toFixed(2)}

Average Loss

${averageLoss.toFixed(2)}

Risk-Reward Ratio

{riskRewardRatio.toFixed(2)}

Maximum Drawdown

{maximumDrawdown.toFixed(2)}%

); }; export default AnalysisDisplay;
